    "MissionGiver": "Covalex Independent Contractors",
    "Title": "Bulk Covalex Shipment Needs Recovering",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nHere's the situation. After spending an hour on comms talking to the hauler, trying to help them diagnose what's wrong with their ship, it's been decided that we now need to get someone to head over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and complete the delivery.\n\nThis is a pretty big one. You'll need a ship that can store <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> and unless you're super strong a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to shift it all.\n\nI would really appreciate if we could just get this one done. Take the cargo to the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4> and we can put this all behind us.\n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.' \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
